description: Nassington is located just north of Fotheringhay in Northamptonshire. Walkers can enjoy some pleasant trails along the River Nene on the Nene Way near the village. This walk takes you along a section of the waymarked path to neighbouring Yarwell and Wansford. Along the way there are nice views of the river and the surrounding countryside to enjoy. Please scroll down for the full list of walks near and around Nassington. The detailed maps below also show a range of footpaths, bridleways and cycle paths in the area.
